光頭佬記招2個主點<br />
Spalletti :Inter cannot sign Rafinha and Joao Cancelo - &quot;we'll see later, but right now we can't&quot;.  No word on his new contract yet. <br />
Spalletti: &quot;I have a contract at Inter and I'm very happy. For me, nothing would have changed had we not made the #UCL. When you're here, you realise that you don't just sign to guarantee your salary. There's no rush to sign the contract.&quot;

